{"tid":1238243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[情緒困擾]大家係唔係好sad","createTime":"2019-06-17T17:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T04:04:53.000Z","uid":168668,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed588b771c5a66a39669ef981c29a78f1401566","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"[sorry for 1999]<br />\n以下為小弟之<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">夢境</span>及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">感想</span>：<br />\n<br />\n今日(17號)我收工7點左右到左龍和道，聽左2個鐘大家分享。<br />\n9點D人過晒去政總鐵馬個邊，我聽到大家係咁叫警察辭職，<br />\n過左冇耐，有班後生女大叫「呀sir過黎啦，我想同你瘋狂傾計」<br />\n「呀sir我地去一齊去摩天輪呀」「呀sir有薯蓉呀，食唔食呀」<br />\n之後我都有附和，一齊叫呀sir飲水、叫呀sir睇後面D車。<br />\n由9點到11點，我地大概氹到5個警察笑(包括1個白衫)。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n我發現到兩樣野：<br />\n<br />\n第一，你屌差佬無疑只會令佢地更團結、更用心思諗點樣殺左你。<br />\n呢幾日政府同警務處割緊蓆，而依家守緊鐵馬既未必係612既前線，<br />\n所以我覺得正是一個時間用「關心」去動搖班散仔。<br />\n<br />\n第二，我覺得第一點其實可以唔理，因為我真正關心既係大家既情緒！<br />\n16號晚我都係政總，我同大家一齊屌狗，但同大家屌完我個心仲係&quot;蟻&quot;住。<br />\n今日我「關心」完警察，反而個情緒舒緩返，呢幾日既壓力都輕鬆左D。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n結論：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得大家可以係唔衝既時候，可以「關心」下班警察，<br />\n係唔<span style=\"color: red;\">放下憤怒</span>既前題，比自己<span style=\"color: red;\">放鬆</span>下，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到衝既時候先屌班盾龜</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n小弟係精神健康服務同工；<br />\n好撚想出文有錢收；<br />\n點都好，用返自己想用既方法；<br />\n我請左no pay leave黎緊日日出。<br />\n<br />\n個夢去到呢道啦，咁大個仔第一次發咁長既夢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[/sorry for 1999]"},{"pid":"49e8e0225e6c9bc3b866b6905be07abaca6c494a","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cfd0e062e0c2f9944447c988d95503092e8c345b","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a8f8556521ed1bf11291f449e627e6da4008e681","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6f96623847f48267b1dc9cce201032ee6ccf20fd","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:50:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e1976b7bb5c032d822513bf49e33d4b1b3d4c894","tid":1238243,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:50:45.000Z","msg":"黑臉白臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e7fcac6252e14455483c9cd8f0c3a83199857a","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"12f6876c8bcf807b2b77a5d7fdc5239951fa9744","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5c82786cce52bd54b16f3404e97ca7e2160df020","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fed1f43f9fe3dd71be5d83c377dc1ff517664315","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"008c15af4012d28cbb41ddba09586f55472aaf87","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae63d48c9f4800b900cf6dbbb0a615aea2a6f4b6","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:55:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d2eaad95cc78bfe2f1b23cb2f055420dc2f3a893","tid":1238243,"uid":78122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"可能你可以感動到佢<br />\n但唔會感動到佢辭職調轉槍頭<br />\n出返嚟邊有咁好人工而又唔洗點做"},{"pid":"62300c0666304bd82041edf2527d27a4f991229f","tid":12