nk target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1238109</a>"},{"pid":"03ded270f7fc474c0a7678a0de3ec0e1589a211c","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"我係諗緊<br />\n當你屌完d警察 你情緒會好高漲<br />\n但當你冇得屌或者屌極都冇反應既時候<br />\n你既情緒會斷層式低落 到時候個感覺會好差"},{"pid":"f6ff2378b3756eae381aed0150078f220bb02c10","tid":1238243,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"其實係兩邊都被人挑撥。無差別咁亂屌其實幾無厘頭。"},{"pid":"338856b36a2780a73222ee1ace448e83d4e5cded","tid":1238243,"uid":168668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"219042bf1b00d276623218f8cd7a223d2e00b60c","tid":1238243,"uid":231090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"有班後生女大叫「呀sir過黎啦，我想同你瘋狂傾計」<br />\n「呀sir我地去一齊去摩天輪呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班女仔咁公然係到flirt仔"},{"pid":"be532076ea3af47bd95a5e51f6a0d69a55d5cfdd","tid":1238243,"uid":32961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"比人打完仲要同佢有傾有笑 我真係做唔到"}]}